name: Hentai Girls: Mommy Milkers
description:
Hentai Girls : Mommy Milkers is a sliding puzzle game, providing a relaxing but comfortably challenging experience. There are 5 girls on the Mommy Milker Farm that each have their own set of puzzles to complete, with varying difficulty as you progress. As you progress, their milkers get bigger and bigger until they're overflowing and shooting everywhere! These titty cows are waiting to feed you their warm milkies!

Features:
- Enjoy a total of 33 puzzles to complete.

- The gallery features photos from the puzzles you completed. View all the sexy mommies, and their milkers, in the gallery!

-Listen to some cheerful music as you complete each puzzle

- Earn achievements by completing the puzzles.
